  .list-item
    .container
        .row
          .span12
            h2 Things We Like
          .span6.center
            <iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/32424882?title=0&amp;byline=0&amp;portrait=0" width="100%" height="300" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe>
            h4 <a href="http://startupweekend.org">Startup Weekend</a>
            p We've competed in <a href="http://startupweekend.org">StartupWeekend</a>s in Southern California. They are excellent events.
          .span6.center
            <iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/38101676?color=00c4ff" width="100%" height="300" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe>
            h4 The Most Astounding Fact
            p Astrophysicist <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neil_deGrasse_Tyson">Dr. Neil DeGrasse Tyson</a> speaks to Connectivity as the most astounding fact.
          .span3 &nbsp;
          .span6.center
            <iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/21837974?badge=0&amp;color=ffffff" width="100%" height="300" frameborder="0" webkitAllowFullScreen mozallowfullscreen allowFullScreen></iframe>
            h4 <a href="http://betahaus.de/">betahaus</a>
